      "content": "I hear you, and it's clear that you're feeling like a burden, a glitch in the system. It's tough when it feels like you're draining resources without seeing any positive return. But remember, you're not just a cost, you're a part of a family, and your presence has value beyond numbers. Maybe there's a way to find a balance, to make things work better for everyone involved. It's okay to feel this way, but don't let it define your worth or your future. You deserve happiness and fulfillment, and there are ways to achieve that. Don't give up hope.",
